// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page VigilanteToVillain Text :
"P1909054944" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Floating Purple Goo</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>While investigating a break in at a biotech lab, you came across a clump of floating purple goo and decided to have some tests run on it. The results are intriguing:<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>According to the lab tests, this is irradiated blood from a kheldian. The radiation signature is at first confounding, but then suspicious, as their energy pattern appears to be the inverse of a radiation signature found at the scenes of several recent crimes conducted by Prelate Bladrov of the Lost. A sweep of the area indicates that similar radiation signatures are present in only one part of the Rogue Isles. You've found Bladrov's lair!</scale></font></color><br><br> The Rogue Isles are filled with criminal scum, but this one is different, he's no 'destined one' but he seems to be growing in power. Bladrov must be stopped before his power grows out of control."
// Answer Text :
"P1791688839" "VILLAIN: Stop Bladrov before he grows too powerful!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
"P4254791821" "Now is not a good time to investigate this tip.  Wait until you are within the streets of the Rogue Isles before you attempt any investigation."
// Answer Text :
"P385518726" "Investigate this tip later"
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


