// Contact Name : Flambeaux's Social Network Page 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Name :
"P4112052336" "Flambeaux's Social Network Page"
// LocationString :
// ProfessionString :
// AskAboutTextOverride :
// ContactRequiresText :
// IDontKnowYouString :
// NoTasksRemainingString :
// PlayerBusyString :
// ComeBackLaterString :
// FailsafeLevelString :

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page VigilanteToVillain Text :
"P2668893068" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Flambeaux's Social Network Page</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You notice an update on Flambeaux's social network page and check it out, interested in a good laugh.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>TheHotChick: Hai guys! I am super excited! =D I am totally  doing the awesomest thing today. Polar Shift and I got these cute little invites from these ancient creepy wizard guys. o_0 I know, I was like ewwwww at first too, but they turned out to be totally awesome. Anyway, so the invites are, I kid you not, on scrolls! Like big roll up scrolls from a kung fu movie or something. They even have these cute little tassles ^_^ I'll totally post pics later.<br><br>So, the invites are for this mystical ceremony being held in our honor that will give us tremendous kick-butt powers! I know, I know, it sounds like a trap, but Polar and I agreed that it was just too cool to pass up, so boys, don't worry, I got a friend to make sure they don't try some creepy stuff. kisses! =*<br><br>IceQueen: You dummy, they said not to tell anyone, now half the internet knows about it. Ugh, you better hope nobody finds out where we are going. -_-; <br><br>TheHotChick: Nobody will be able to find this place. Do you know how many miles of caves there are under the city? Let alone ones filled with creepy wizard dudes. =p<br><br>IceQueen: u_u *sigh*<br><br>DeanMan: Hey ladies, if you want I can be on call to swing by in case things get weird. I'll message you my number. Stay hot, sexy.<br><br>TheHotChick: Awwww Thnx Dean! =D I got the message, I'll text you later and let you know how things are going. *kisses* =*<br><br>DeanMan: giggidy<br><br>TheHotChick: LOL<br><br>IceQueen: Get a room.</scale></font></color><br><br> Anyway, that exchange has 23 more comments, none of which offer any useful information... to anyone. Mystic ceremony, super "kick-butt" powers? There is no way that a witless moron like Flambeaux is getting her hands on free power when you would be a far better choice. All you have to do is figure out where they went.<br><br>Dumb as she is, Flambeaux wouldn't trust the Circle of Thorns, and the Midnight Squad doesn't hang out in caves... often. She must be talking about the Legacy Chain. It shouldn't be too hard to track down where they are going. The Legacy Chain doesn't have the largest following, so they could only be in a handful of places. You'd better hurry up, that first post by Flambeaux was 4 hours old, they're probably already on their way."
// Answer Text :
"P2703386778" "VILLAIN: Take the mystic power for yourself"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


