// Contact Name : A Siren's Call 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Name :
"P4105383766" "A Siren's Call"
// LocationString :
// ProfessionString :
// AskAboutTextOverride :
// ContactRequiresText :
// IDontKnowYouString :
// NoTasksRemainingString :
// PlayerBusyString :
// ComeBackLaterString :
// FailsafeLevelString :

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page VigilanteToVillain Text :
"P3319768863" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Siren's Call</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Your phone rings and when you answer all you hear is static. As you are about to hang up you hear a woman's voice faintly through the interference.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>{HeroName}, *static* Savage Si*static*. I *static* your help. *static* tracking *static*, found her with *static*-show. *static* stupid sewers. I'm near *static*-37. Too many Freaks, *static* use your *static*. Ugh, *static* text you!</scale></font></color><br><br> From what you could pick out of the static it sounds like Savage Siren has been tracking someone with the Freakshow to the sewers. She said it was a she, so you think it must be Clamour. No wonder Savage Siren needs your help, Clamour is no pushover. You got her text message and it says to enter the sewers at junction 1237. Together you can take down Clamour and make her pay for her crimes!"
// Answer Text :
"P3331906052" "VILLAIN: Help Savage Siren eliminate Clamour!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


